&mo 1      &kp GRAVE  &kp CAPS  &kp LEFT  &kp RIGHT          &kp BSPC  &kp DEL    &kp END       &kp PG_DN  &kp ENTER  &kp KP_N0          &kp UP      &kp DOWN      &kp KP_DOT     &kp RBKT         &mo 1
            >;
